Name: The Guild Garage
Title: Panhard Lemon
Desc: Janice is speechless when David purchases a 1952 Panhard Dyna Brake Station Wagon.
LongDescription: Janice is speechless when David purchases a 1952 Panhard Dyna Brake Station Wagon at the Concours d'Lemon in California, but has plenty to say when the lemon is delivered to The Guild; David gets an unusual request from the Canadian Armed Forces.
